data.title: Tehran Times
data.text:
2024-07-06 22:41

Jules Verne’s “The Green Ray” available in bookstores

TEHRAN-The Persian translation of the novel “The Green Ray” written by the French author Jules Verne has been released in the Iranian book market.

2024-04-01 20:00

Jules Verne’s “The Carpathian Castle” hits bookstores

TEHRAN-A Persian translation of the novel “The Carpathian Castle” written by the French author Jules Verne has been released in the bookstores across the country.

2023-09-07 21:32

Jules Verne’s “Dick Sand, A Captain at Fifteen” published in Persian

TEHRAN-Qoqnoos Publishing Group has released the Persian translation of Jules Verne’s novel “Dick Sand, A Captain at Fifteen” in Iran under the title “The Fifteen-Year-Old Captain”.

2022-02-05 19:09

Jules Verne’s “The Begum’s Millions” published in Persian

TEHRAN – French writer Jules Verne’s novel “The Begum’s Millions”, also published as “The Begum’s Fortune”, has been published in Persian.
